  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5a5e9455413ed000145c34c3",
      "text": "キャズム理論",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516147800,
      "updated": 1516147800
    },
    {
      "id": "5a5e9458aff09e0000a8893a",
      "text": "正確に言えば[イノベーター理論]だが世の中の知名度は[キャズム]の方が上だろう。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516147800,
      "updated": 1516601042
    },
    {
      "id": "5a5e959eaff09e0000a88951",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/a81072f92da6c4f9021fa763958f349e]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516148126,
      "updated": 1516148126
    },
    {
      "id": "5a5e9468aff09e0000a8893c",
      "text": "[Diffusion of innovations - Wikipedia https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diffusion_of_innovations]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516147817,
      "updated": 1516148142
    },
    {
      "id": "5a657ed8aff09e0000e7700d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516601048,
      "updated": 1516601048
    },
    {
      "id": "5a5e95afaff09e0000a88952",
      "text": " イノベーター理論",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516148144,
      "updated": 1516601053
    },
    {
      "id": "5a5e9469aff09e0000a8893d",
      "text": "  [Everett M. Rogers] が提唱",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516147817,
      "updated": 1554825325
    },
    {
      "id": "5a5e94acaff09e0000a88948",
      "text": "  1962",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516147884,
      "updated": 1516601057
    },
    {
      "id": "5a5e94aeaff09e0000a88949",
      "text": "  商品購入の態度を購入タイミングの早い順に五つに分類",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516147886,
      "updated": 1516601057
    },
    {
      "id": "5a5e9469aff09e0000a8893f",
      "text": "   [イノベーター]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516147817,
      "updated": 1516601057
    },
    {
      "id": "5a5e94d6aff09e0000a8894a",
      "text": "   [アーリーアダプター]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516147926,
      "updated": 1516601057
    },
    {
      "id": "5a5e94dbaff09e0000a8894c",
      "text": "   [アーリーマジョリティ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516147932,
      "updated": 1516601057
    },
    {
      "id": "5a5e94e4aff09e0000a8894d",
      "text": "   [レイトマジョリティ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516147941,
      "updated": 1516601057
    },
    {
      "id": "5a5e94ecaff09e0000a8894e",
      "text": "   [ラガード]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516147948,
      "updated": 1516601057
    },
    {
      "id": "607a57eeaff09e00008b4192",
      "text": " ちなみに「16%のラガードがいる」みたいに「何らかの理由で分類が決まって、その人の割合を調べたら何%だった」という説明の仕方をしている人はちゃんと理解できてない人",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1618630639,
      "updated": 1618630810
    },
    {
      "id": "607a5847aff09e00008b4193",
      "text": " 　「下位16%をラガードと定義した」が正しい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1618630728,
      "updated": 1618630839
    },
    {
      "id": "607a58b7aff09e00008b4194",
      "text": " 　16%という「キリが良くないように見える数字」に何か深い意味があると思い込んでしまってる人がいるが、単に正規分布をキリがいい標準偏差の整数倍で切っただけである",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1618630840,
      "updated": 1618630912
    },
    {
      "id": "5a5e952aaff09e0000a8894f",
      "text": " \t[https://gyazo.com/a309d6e77e47a3430508fb81e9f334f4]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516148010,
      "updated": 1618630524
    },
    {
      "id": "607a5760aff09e0000d20535",
      "text": " \t\t[Diffusion of Innovations] p.243",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1618630497,
      "updated": 1618630524
    },
    {
      "id": "607a590eaff09e00008b4195",
      "text": " \t\t新技術の採用はS字カーブを描くので、採用の頻度はベル状の曲線になる、だからこれを正規分布で近似する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1618630926,
      "updated": 1618631020
    },
    {
      "id": "607a57b6aff09e0000d20536",
      "text": " \t[https://gyazo.com/7c1f4c9c357119c506eaa270ffd009e5]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1618630583,
      "updated": 1618630585
    },
    {
      "id": "607a57b8aff09e0000d20537",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1618630585,
      "updated": 1618630585
    },
    {
      "id": "607a575daff09e0000d20534",
      "text": "\t\t\tp. 247",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1618630494,
      "updated": 1618630592
    },
    {
      "id": "607a596faff09e00008b4196",
      "text": "\t\t\t正規分布を標準偏差の整数倍のところで5つに切り分けて名前をつけた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1618631024,
      "updated": 1618631061
    },
    {
      "id": "607a57c1aff09e0000d20538",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1618630593,
      "updated": 1618630593
    },
    {
      "id": "5a5e94d6aff09e0000a8894b",
      "text": "\t後に書籍「[キャズム]」で「アーリーアダプターとアーリーマジョリティの間の溝(キャズム)が深い」という主張がなされる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516147926,
      "updated": 1618630041
    },
    {
      "id": "5ac8d7e6aff09e0000ac44db",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523111910,
      "updated": 1523111910
    },
    {
      "id": "5a5e952caff09e0000a88950",
      "text": "\t[何がラガードを遅らせるのか]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516148013,
      "updated": 1523111908
    },
